 \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions_wrestling\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In any other era, Penn State's Joe Kovacs would be the greatest shot-putter of his day.\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1138, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1069, \"end\": 1079, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions_wrestling\", \"score\": 0.9992962580016969, \"rank\": 0.0007042375227208816, \"text\": \"Penn State\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions_wrestling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions_wrestling\"}, {\"begin\": 1082, \"end\": 1085, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\", \"score\": 0.9996443899151922, \"rank\": 0.0003390798135727977, \"text\": \"Joe\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Kovacs has spent a decade competing against Ryan Crouser, who became the first three-time Olympic shot-put champ in Paris.\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1270, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1192, \"end\": 1204, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Crouser\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ryan Crouser\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Crouser\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Crouser\"}, {\"begin\": 1264, \"end\": 1269, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999962256, \"rank\": 3.770454752504876e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And Kovacs won his third silver medal alongside Crouser.\", \"from\": 1271, \"to\": 1327, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He did so dramatically.\", \"from\": 1329, \"to\": 1352, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Penn State graduate and two-time world champion hit a throw of 22.15 meters on his final attempt to claim the silver.\", \"from\": 1353, \"to\": 1474, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1357, \"end\": 1367, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions_wrestling\", \"score\": 0.9992962580016969, \"rank\": 0.0007042375227208816, \"text\": \"Penn State\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions_wrestling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions_wrestling\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 35-year-old Kovacs continued a marvelous career in Paris, winning his ninth international medal since 2015.\", \"from\": 1475, \"to\": 1586, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1530, \"end\": 1535, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999962256, \"rank\": 3.770454752504876e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Did you know about Stephen Nedoroscik before the Olympics?\", \"from\": 1588, \"to\": 1646, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1607, \"end\": 1625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Nedoroscik\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stephen Nedoroscik\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Nedoroscik\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Nedoroscik\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Did you know there was such a thing as a pommel horse specialist?\", \"from\": 1647, \"to\": 1712, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Penn State graduate, and 2021 world champ, became a first-week star of the Paris Olympics when he won two bronze medals in men's gymnastics.\", \"from\": 1713, \"to\": 1857, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1717, \"end\": 1727, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penn_State_Nittany_Lions_wrestling\", \"score\": 0.9992962580016969, \"rank\": 0.0007042375227208816, \"text\": \"Penn St